title: Simone Biles answers some quarantine questions from her Texan home
description:
Four-time Olympic champion gymnast Simone Biles joined the Olympic Channel to talk about her COVID-19 challenges, receiving a call from Vogue editor Anna Wintour, and what she has been working on since her return to the gym.

The interview was part of our one year to go celebrations. For more interview with Simone and over 100 more amazing Olympians - head to olympicchannel.com/podcast
